::Aerotaur::
       "I think I'm okay Starstomp.  I should be able to get this fixed 
before too long."  He reconnects some more cables and the lights come on 
replacing the emergency lights.  "Well, that helps."  He hears a noise in the 
room and looks around.  In the new light he sees the survivor standing 
nearby, eyes glowing.  "I think I found a survivor."  He turns around very 
slowly.  "Hi.  I'm Aerotaur.  And you are?"

--part1_f.1bde2a7a.28efd2c1_boundary
